     4ÔåÆuse super::{Either, Left, Right};
     6ÔåÆ/// Provides methods for converting a type `Self` into either a [`Left`] or [`Right`]
     7ÔåÆ/// variant of [`Either<Self, Self>`](Either).
     8ÔåÆ///
     9ÔåÆ/// The [`into_either`](IntoEither::into_either) method takes a [`bool`] to determine
